<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَبَادَرْتُ مِنْه النَّأَيَ وَالْمَرْءُ قَادِرٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَلَى سَهْمِهْ مَا دَامَ فِي كَفِّهِ السَّهْمُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَيَشْتِمُ عِرْضِي فِي الْمَغَيَّبِ جَاهِدًا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلَيْسَ لَهُ عِنْدِي هَوَانٌ وَلا شَتْمُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِذَا سُمْتُهُ وَصْلَ الْقَرَابَةِ سَامَنِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>قَطِيعَتَهَا تِلْكَ السَّفَاهَةُ وَالإِثْمُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَإِنْ أَدْعُهُ لِلنِّصْفِ يَأْبَى وَيَعْصِنِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَيَدْعُو لِحُكْمِ جَائِر غَيْرُهْ الْحُكْمُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَلَوْلا اتِّقَاءُ الله وَالرَّحِمِ اللَّتِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>رِعَايَتُهَا حَقٌّ وَتَعْطِيلُهَا ظُلْمُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِذَا لِعُلاهُ بَارِقِي وَخَطْمَتُهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِوَسْمِ شِنَارٍ لا يُشَابِهُهُ وَسْمُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَيَسْعَى إِذَا أَبْنِي لِهَّدْمِ مَصَالِحِي<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَلَيْسَ الذِّي يَبْنِي كَمَنْ شَأْنُهُ الْهَدْمُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>يَوَدُّ لَوْ أَنِّي مُعْدِمٌ ذُوْ خَصَاصَةٍ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَأَكْرَهُ جُهْدِي إِنْ يُخَالِطَهُ الْعُدْمُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَيَعْتَدُ غَنْمًا فِي الْحَوَادِثِ نَكْبَتِي<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَمَا إِنْ لَهُ فِيْهَا سَنَاءٌ وَلا غُنْمُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَمَا زِلْتُ فِي لَيْنِي لَهُ وَتَعَطُفِيْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>عَلَيْهِ كَمَا تَحْنُو على الْوَلَدُ الأُمُّ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَخَفْضٍ لَهُ مِنِّي الْجَنَاحَ تَأَلُفًا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>لِتُدْنِيَهُ مِنّي الْقَرَابَةُ وَالرَّحْمُ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>